		    checkmail INSTALL HOWTO

1) uudeview
 checkmail depend on uudeview program (http://www.uni-frankfurt.de/~fp/uudeview/)
 You can remove uudeview support by simple code correction

2) compilation procedure
  ./configure
  make
  copy chekmail executable in /usr/local/sbin

3) sendmail m4 install
  add this lines to your .mc file
  
dnl Change Mlocal
define(`LOCAL_MAILER_PATH', `/usr/local/sbin/checkmail')dnl
define(`LOCAL_MAILER_ARGS', `checkmail -d $u,
		U=root:mail')
MODIFY_MAILER_FLAGS(`LOCAL', `-m')dnl

4) sendmail .cf install
 Chage block for Mlocal to this

Mlocal,		P=/usr/local/sbin/checkmail, F=lsDFMAw5:/|@qPrn9, S=EnvFromL/HdrFromL, R=EnvToL/HdrToL,
		T=DNS/RFC822/X-Unix,
		A=checkmail -d $u,
		U=root:mail

5) postfix install
 Add or change mailbox_command in your main.cf to this

 mailbox_command = /usr/local/sbin/checkmail -d $USER

